            </div>
            <div>
                <p style="color: white;">Below are some forum usage guidelines. They are posted here as a general reminder in an effort to keep the forums friendly and usable for everyone.  The forums are for everyone, new and advanced users alike.
            </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center" style=" width: 100%;">
            <div class=" topspacingforum">
                <div class="forumsubheaders">
                    <h2 style="color: #ffffff;"  class="roboto-condensed">News</h2>
                </div>
                <div id="news" class="forumsections " style="height: 300px;" >
                    <a href="https://www.l4d.com/blog/"  > 
                        <div class="overlay d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                            <div ><span class="greenselected">More Info</span> about left 4 Dead</div>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center align-items-md-start  flex-md-row gap-3 row-gap-3 ">
            <div class="topspacingforum">
                <div class="forumsubheaders">
